OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FPrivate workers' pay growth
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Foutpaces public sector     
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The gap between wage growth in the     
OL,6, public and private sector is near a    
OL,7, record high, official figures show.    
OL,9,FWorkers in the private sector saw their
OL,10,Faverage pay rise by 6.9% between August
OL,11,Fand October, according to the Office   
OL,12,Ffor National Statistics (ONS).         
OL,14,FThat compares to wage growth of just   
OL,15,F2.7% for public sector employees.      
OL,17,FThousands of workers are set to go on  
OL,18,Fstrike this week, including nurses who 
OL,19,Fexpect to stage their first-ever       
OL,20,Fnationwide walkout on Thursday.        
